 all this information was found.

3
00:00:05.480 --> 00:00:08.440
Do us all a favour
 and make sure it don't happen again.

4
00:00:09.240 --> 00:00:12.480
Better turn on two factor authentication
 and make it harder in future.

5
00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:15.760
Since most websites have,
 it is practically a guarantee that

6
00:00:15.760 --> 00:00:16.840
FriendlyBook has.

7
00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:19.560
She's probably already
 got a code generator somewhere.

8
00:00:20.080 --> 00:00:22.120
I'll email you through
 if I find anything more.

